Fit a homogeneous poisson process

fithpp.Rd

Compute maximum likelihood estimator for the hpp model with time events

fithpp(events)

Arguments

events

vector containing the event times.

Value

an hpp object fitted

Examples

pois_y <- hpp(lambda = 1)
events <- simulatehpp(pois_y, end=10)

#> Simulating up to endtime. To simulate n events specify n.
fithpp(events)
